*Izvolite* da vam pomognem. (Here you are, let me help you.)
*Izvolite* li da vam pokažem? (Would you like me to show you?)
*Izvolite* li da čekate ovde? (Would you like to wait here?)
*Izvolite* da vam pokažem svoje delo? (May I show you my work?)
*Izvolite* li da vam predstavim? (Would you like me to introduce myself?)